      "content": "i just don't feel comfortable with that. my blood sugar is already looking a bit low right now because i didn't eat. if i take the full dose now, i'm almost certain i'll wake up in a bad way. can't i just take half the dose or just skip it entirely this once? it seems more logical than forcing insulin in when there's no glucose to process.",
